{
  "title": "Mouthwatering Garlicky Saudi Arabian Lamb Kebabs",
  "description": "Juicy lamb kebabs marinated in a garlicky mixture and grilled to perfection in a tandoor, served in a bento box with a sprinkle of pecorino romano cheese.",
  "cuisine": "Saudi Arabian",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
